      <title>波士顿市长提高商业地产税的计划遭遇阻碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/boston-mayor-s-plan-to-raise-commercial-property-taxes-hits-snag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长 Michelle Wu 暂时提高商业地产税的计划再次受阻，因为新数据显示办公楼价值下跌对该市税收体系的影响不会像最初估计的那么严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/boston-mayor-s-plan-to-raise-commercial-property-taxes-hits-snag</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 21:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙誓言完成法国总统剩余任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/macron-says-he-will-serve-out-remainder-of-his-term-until-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，他将完成剩余总统任期，他希望尽快平息玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党与左翼议员联手推翻其政府后法国出现的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/macron-says-he-will-serve-out-remainder-of-his-term-until-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:20:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党中国事务委员会主席抨击美国对华为芯片限制存在“漏洞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gop-china-panel-chair-slams-us-chip-curbs-for-huawei-loopholes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院一位重要共和党人批评了拜登政府遏制中国芯片制造野心的最新举动，称周一公布的美国规则留下了漏洞，使华为技术有限公司等中国公司能够继续获取美国技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gop-china-panel-chair-slams-us-chip-curbs-for-huawei-loopholes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 17:51:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚新​​任财政部长称，左翼分子忽视宏观稳定就会失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/new-colombia-finance-chief-says-leftist-leaders-fail-when-they-neglect-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚新​​任财政部长表示，如果不能保证宏观经济稳定，拉丁美洲的进步政府注定会失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/new-colombia-finance-chief-says-leftist-leaders-fail-when-they-neglect-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 17:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里对巴里克黄金公司首席执行官马克·布里斯托发出逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/mali-issues-arrest-warrant-for-barrick-gold-ceo-mark-bristow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在西非国家矿山收入纠纷不断升级的背景下，马里军方控制的政府已向巴里克黄金公司首席执行官马克·布里斯托发出了洗钱逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/mali-issues-arrest-warrant-for-barrick-gold-ceo-mark-bristow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 16:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员恩斯特拒绝支持赫格塞斯，让陷入困境的候选人陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gop-senator-ernst-declines-to-back-hegseth-leaving-embattled-nominee-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院共和党人乔尼·恩斯特 (Joni Ernst) 是一名战斗老兵和强奸幸存者，在军事问题上对共和党同事有影响力，他明确拒绝支持皮特·赫格塞斯 (Pete Hegseth) 陷入困境的国防部长提名，并呼吁对针对他的指控进行进一步调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gop-senator-ernst-declines-to-back-hegseth-leaving-embattled-nominee-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果马克龙放宽债务路径，勒庞将在未来几周内公布法国预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/le-pen-france-budget-likely-within-weeks-if-macron-eases-debt-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞表示，只要下一任总理准备以更慢的速度缩小赤字，法国就能克服政府垮台并在“几周内”出台预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/le-pen-france-budget-likely-within-weeks-if-macron-eases-debt-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 13:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冯德莱恩前往南方共同市场峰会之际，欧盟接近与南方共同市场达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/von-der-leyen-to-attend-mercosur-summit-with-eu-trade-deal-close</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩抵达乌拉圭参加南方共同市场峰会，欧盟旨在与拉丁美洲主要国家达成一项长期寻求的贸易协议。]]></description>
